<BaseLayout
  title="Vernal Medicare Office at Smith's Pharmacy | Visit Our Local Agent"
  description="Visit Vernal Medicare inside Smith's Pharmacy at 1080 W Hwy 40 in Vernal, UT. Stop in, call, or schedule a home visit. Free plan reviews. Mon–Fri 1pm–5pm. Call 435-219-5120."
